First version homepage hosted on commecial web hosting with domain duguo.com. online@duguo.com is my main contact on internet from then. There are lots of social feature such as online mobile message, msn status and message integratation. All based on my personal project XDirectory.

At 2007, I bought a dedicated virtual server. And deployed mediawiki as my homepage base. It depends on yahoo pipes to aggregated bookmark and albums feed and then display on my homepage. Guo Du is a software engineer in Lotus Connections Homepage team at IBM Dublin Software Laboratory. He hold different roles in IBM Lotus social and collaboration software development, system test and support in past three years.

Prior to IBM, Guo worked at NewBay Software for two and half years, where he developed mobile share/blog/messaging core systems for leading mobile operators. NewBay's engineering team expanded from 20+ to 100+ during his serve.

Guo graduated from Dublin City University(Ireland) with a Master degree in eCommerce and from Dalian University of Technology(China) with a BS degree in Management Information System.

At spare time, he participate discussions in open source projects. More information in CV: Guo Du and LinkedIn Profile.
